Hi there, 
First of before we begin: This is my very very first guide so [u]please do not hate.[/u]

This command will only be avaible for Extreme Donators, not Regular Donators.
Okay, today i'm going to learn you guys how to add a Extreme Donator command.

Under:
[code]			if (cmd[0].equalsIgnoreCase("You have to be a Extreme Donator to use this!")) {[/code]

Add:
[code]				if (player.isExtremeDonator()) {[/code]

There we go we've just made a Extreme Donator only command:

[code]			if (cmd[0].equalsIgnoreCase("COMMAND_HERE")) {
				if (player.isExtremeDonator()) {
						player.sendMessage("TEXT_HERE");
		                		return true;
		            	}[/code]

Also you can make a messege telling the Regular Donators, that they're not allowed to use this command:

[code]					if (!player.isExtremeDonator()) {
						player.sendMessage("You have to be a Extreme Donator to use this!");
[/code]

Thank-you alot for using my Snippet!
